<p style="float: right; width: 200px; padding: 1em; margin: 1em; border: 2px dotted red;">
Please use the wiki formatting sparingly!<br/><br/> The wiki formatting is intended to give a some flexibility for
annotations and should not interfere with the rest of the page layout.
</p>
<h4>Wiki Formatting</h4>
<p style="margin-left: 2em">
<b>Emphasis</b>
<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;''italics''; '''bold'''; '''''bold italics'''''; ---- horizontal rule 
<br>
<b>Headings</b>
<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;=&nbsp;Title&nbsp;1&nbsp;=; ==&nbsp;Title&nbsp;2&nbsp;==; ===&nbsp;Title&nbsp;3&nbsp;===
<br>
<b>Lists</b>
<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;tab or 4 spaces and: * bullets; 1., a., A., i., I. numbered items; spaces alone indent 
<br>
<b>Links</b>
<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp; url; [url]; [url|label]
</p>
